1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:12,000
(Watch on www.kisskh.li Support Admin)

2
00:00:07,060 --> 00:00:08,180
Shen Gu,

3
00:00:10,740 --> 00:00:12,820
will you consider my proposal?

4
00:00:30,820 --> 00:00:32,339
Miss Xu, Mr. Xu is in critical condition!

5
00:00:32,340 --> 00:00:33,800
He needs to be sent
to the hospital now!

6
00:01:17,600 --> 00:01:21,519
=Echoes of Gang City=

7
00:01:21,520 --> 00:01:24,599
=Episode 2=
(I Saw You in My Dreams)

8
00:01:24,600 --> 00:01:27,080
(Gang City Central Hospital)

9
00:01:39,900 --> 00:01:41,220
- Doctor.
- Doctor.

10
00:01:41,260 --> 00:01:42,579
How's my grandfather?

11
00:01:42,580 --> 00:01:44,259
He's out of danger now.

12
00:01:44,260 --> 00:01:46,379
Mr. Xu is nearly a hundred years old.

13
00:01:46,380 --> 00:01:47,579
His heart and lung reserves,

14
00:01:47,580 --> 00:01:49,579
as well as his recovery ability,
are very weak.

15
00:01:49,580 --> 00:01:50,459
The surgery

16
00:01:50,460 --> 00:01:52,760
could have caused severe complications.

17
00:01:52,760 --> 00:01:55,000
Fortunately, Mr. Shen brought in
the country's top specialist

18
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:57,060
from City A yesterday,

19
00:01:57,460 --> 00:02:00,380
so the operation could
be carried out in time and effectively.

20
00:02:00,940 --> 00:02:02,060
Thank you for your hard work.

21
00:02:02,340 --> 00:02:02,859
Thank you.

22
00:02:02,860 --> 00:02:04,019
Don't let us keep you.

23
00:02:04,020 --> 00:02:04,740
Thank you.

24
00:02:05,260 --> 00:02:06,460
Thank you.

25
00:02:06,780 --> 00:02:07,940
Don't mention it.

26
00:02:08,180 --> 00:02:10,340
You're putting in so much effort
for my dad.

27
00:02:10,500 --> 00:02:13,100
Are you looking for a way
to get close to the Xu family?

28
00:02:13,300 --> 00:02:14,500
Uncle Zhaohui,

29
00:02:14,540 --> 00:02:16,340
he saved Grandfather.

30
00:02:17,500 --> 00:02:18,619
He suddenly turns into

31
00:02:18,620 --> 00:02:20,499
the largest shareholder of Junlin Group.

32
00:02:20,500 --> 00:02:21,459
Who's to say

33
00:02:21,460 --> 00:02:23,139
he won't set his sights

34
00:02:23,140 --> 00:02:25,940
on our family's assets next?

35
00:02:26,540 --> 00:02:27,219
Wanxin,

36
00:02:27,220 --> 00:02:28,979
I have a good assessment of people.

37
00:02:28,980 --> 00:02:29,939
You should

38
00:02:29,940 --> 00:02:30,979
keep your distance from him.

39
00:02:30,980 --> 00:02:33,220
Since Mr. Xu's stable now,

40
00:02:33,540 --> 00:02:34,940
I won't disturb you further.

41
00:02:35,260 --> 00:02:36,260
See yourself out.

42
00:02:36,980 --> 00:02:38,060
I'll walk him out.

43
00:02:38,540 --> 00:02:39,379
Wanxin.

44
00:02:39,380 --> 00:02:39,779
Wanxin.

45
00:02:39,780 --> 00:02:40,419
Uncle Zhaohui.

46
00:02:40,420 --> 00:02:41,459
(Third Floor, Operating Room)

47
00:02:41,460 --> 00:02:43,220
You should stay
and wait for Grandfather.

48
00:02:50,191 --> 00:02:51,420
Mr. Shen.

49
00:02:53,180 --> 00:02:54,500
I'm sorry about that.

50
00:02:54,940 --> 00:02:56,980
I apologize for my uncle.

51
00:02:58,340 --> 00:03:00,020
You don't need to apologize for anyone.

52
00:03:02,076 --> 00:03:03,140
Wanxin.

53
00:03:07,060 --> 00:03:07,899
There was an incident

54
00:03:07,900 --> 00:03:10,740
while your dad's body
was being transported back to Gang City.

55
00:03:10,900 --> 00:03:13,099
Mr. Shen helped coordinate everything.

56
00:03:13,100 --> 00:03:15,300
The body has now been placed
at the funeral home.

57
00:03:17,620 --> 00:03:19,300
There are also a few documents here

58
00:03:20,220 --> 00:03:21,940
that you need to sign.

59
00:03:24,320 --> 00:03:27,280
(Gang City Public Mortuary,
Department of Health)

60
00:03:29,040 --> 00:03:34,440
(Gang City Public Mortuary,
Department of Health)

61
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:52,320
(Family Confirmation and Signature)

62
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:01,040
(Xu)

63
00:04:13,780 --> 00:04:14,860
Excuse me.

64
00:04:16,300 --> 00:04:17,420
I need a moment.

65
00:04:59,580 --> 00:05:00,900
Uncle Zhaohui.

66
00:05:01,020 --> 00:05:02,859
Hello, Hao?

67
00:05:02,860 --> 00:05:03,860
What are you doing?

68
00:05:04,220 --> 00:05:06,490
I'm busy preparing for the wedding.

69
00:05:07,300 --> 00:05:08,900
At a time like this?

70
00:05:10,260 --> 00:05:12,419
Don't say I didn't warn you.

71
00:05:12,420 --> 00:05:14,079
My father is hospitalized.

72
00:05:14,080 --> 00:05:16,139
Even Shen Gu showed up to help.

73
00:05:16,140 --> 00:05:18,299
No matter how busy you are,
you should come by.

74
00:05:18,300 --> 00:05:20,579
This is an important stage
for you and Wanxin.

75
00:05:20,580 --> 00:05:22,379
You need to show your sincerity.

76
00:05:22,380 --> 00:05:23,740
Shen Gu?

77
00:05:23,980 --> 00:05:25,180
What is he doing there?

78
00:05:25,300 --> 00:05:26,539
What is he doing here?

79
00:05:26,540 --> 00:05:28,460
You should know that better than anyone.

80
00:05:35,580 --> 00:05:39,019
Mr. Shen, I'm really grateful
for everything you've done

81
00:05:39,020 --> 00:05:40,580
for my grandfather and dad.

82
00:05:42,700 --> 00:05:44,620
My uncle's words don't represent me.

83
00:05:45,140 --> 00:05:46,260
So,

84
00:05:47,380 --> 00:05:48,940
have you considered

85
00:05:49,740 --> 00:05:51,180
my proposal?

86
00:06:13,380 --> 00:06:14,500
Sorry.

87
00:06:15,700 --> 00:06:16,499
Hi.

88
00:06:16,500 --> 00:06:17,580
Hello?

89
00:06:18,820 --> 00:06:21,940
We are the Legal Department
of Qingniao Group.

90
00:06:23,420 --> 00:06:25,700
Okay. I see.

91
00:06:25,740 --> 00:06:27,500
I'll check it immediately.

92
00:06:27,940 --> 00:06:29,060
Thank you.

93
00:06:29,500 --> 00:06:30,580
Okay.

94
00:06:33,320 --> 00:06:34,379
(Qingniao Group Investment Contract)

95
00:06:34,380 --> 00:06:36,140
(Dear Miss Xu Wanxin,)

96
00:06:36,380 --> 00:06:37,580
(please accept our condolences.)

97
00:06:38,740 --> 00:06:39,699
(Mr. Xu Zhaoming)

98
00:06:39,700 --> 00:06:42,620
(had signed an agreement with Qingniao Group
before his passing.)

99
00:06:42,860 --> 00:06:44,340
(Due to unforeseen circumstances,)

100
00:06:44,420 --> 00:06:45,940
(Qingniao Group)

101
00:06:46,260 --> 00:06:49,059
(has reassigned the liaison to you...)

102
00:06:49,060 --> 00:06:50,139
(Xu Zhaoming)

103
00:06:50,140 --> 00:06:52,380
(and will continue the investment.)

104
00:06:52,500 --> 00:06:54,919
(Please contact us as soon as possible.)

105
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:58,840
(Total investment is 5.2 billion.)

106
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:03,640
Arrange for the company to notify Xu Wanxin
about the partnership

107
00:07:03,640 --> 00:07:05,400
as soon as her grandfather's
surgery is done.

108
00:07:05,460 --> 00:07:06,379
Shen Gu,

109
00:07:06,380 --> 00:07:07,940
I need to warn you about this.

110
00:07:08,140 --> 00:07:10,459
Aren't you worried
that with Qingniao's contract,

111
00:07:10,460 --> 00:07:12,060
she might not marry you?

112
00:07:12,460 --> 00:07:14,459
What matters now isn't marrying me.

113
00:07:14,460 --> 00:07:16,260
It's helping her get through this.

114
00:07:26,980 --> 00:07:28,100
Mr. Shen,

115
00:07:29,100 --> 00:07:30,500
will you say yes?

116
00:07:41,220 --> 00:07:42,460
Yes, I will.

117
00:07:58,260 --> 00:07:59,179
Mr. Shen,

118
00:07:59,180 --> 00:08:00,860
below us is Gang City.

119
00:08:00,880 --> 00:08:03,960
(One day earlier)

120
00:08:10,340 --> 00:08:11,420
Shen Gu,

121
00:08:12,580 --> 00:08:14,400
you pushed me to the front
all these years

122
00:08:14,400 --> 00:08:16,160
while you expanded the market
behind the scene

123
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:17,459
and laid groundwork in Gang City.

124
00:08:17,460 --> 00:08:19,340
Was it really
all because of Shen Tingyuan?

125
00:08:19,580 --> 00:08:20,980
Or was it because

126
00:08:21,140 --> 00:08:22,939
you wanted to stand before

127
00:08:22,940 --> 00:08:24,620
Miss Xu Wanxin as soon as possible?

128
00:08:24,870 --> 00:08:25,940
Answer me.

129
00:08:27,900 --> 00:08:29,220
Because you're a good actor.

130
00:08:33,660 --> 00:08:34,659
Boss,

131
00:08:34,660 --> 00:08:36,299
Mr. Xu's plane has gone off radar.

132
00:08:36,300 --> 00:08:40,499
CEO of Minghui Group, Mr. Xu Zhaoming,

133
00:08:40,500 --> 00:08:42,459
was involved

134
00:08:42,460 --> 00:08:43,399
in a helicopter crash

135
00:08:43,400 --> 00:08:45,219
and died at the age of 57.

136
00:08:45,220 --> 00:08:46,660
We've also received news

137
00:08:47,540 --> 00:08:48,860
from Gang City.

138
00:08:50,860 --> 00:08:52,980
Chairman Xu collapsed into a coma

139
00:08:53,380 --> 00:08:54,580
after hearing the news.

140
00:08:55,660 --> 00:08:57,539
This sudden and heavy blow

141
00:08:57,540 --> 00:09:00,660
will definitely impact the company.

142
00:09:01,300 --> 00:09:03,980
Both the stock market
and internal operations will be affected.

143
00:09:04,980 --> 00:09:06,220
Change the flight path.

144
00:09:06,620 --> 00:09:07,780
We're returning to Gang City.

145
00:09:10,220 --> 00:09:12,340
Wanxin is dealing with too much
right now.

146
00:09:12,660 --> 00:09:13,419
Shen Gu,

147
00:09:13,420 --> 00:09:14,900
I understand how you feel,

148
00:09:15,100 --> 00:09:17,219
but going back now

149
00:09:17,220 --> 00:09:19,659
means facing Shen Tingyuan
ahead of time.

150
00:09:19,660 --> 00:09:21,179
This isn't the best timing

151
00:09:21,180 --> 00:09:22,620
for both you and Qingniao.

152
00:09:22,780 --> 00:09:24,220
Are you sure?

153
00:09:24,340 --> 00:09:26,539
Rerouting will take time.

154
00:09:26,540 --> 00:09:28,380
Request an emergency landing.

155
00:09:29,260 --> 00:09:31,980
We return as fast as possible.

156
00:09:41,460 --> 00:09:42,660
So you finally came back.

157
00:09:43,980 --> 00:09:45,899
The company has reached out
to Xu Wanxin.

158
00:09:45,900 --> 00:09:47,220
And then?

159
00:09:49,420 --> 00:09:51,420
She proposed to me.

160
00:09:53,900 --> 00:09:55,340
And I accepted.

161
00:10:12,900 --> 00:10:13,980
Shen Gu,

162
00:10:14,140 --> 00:10:16,980
do you know that forging
official documents is illegal?

163
00:10:17,500 --> 00:10:18,740
As you can see,

164
00:10:19,020 --> 00:10:20,610
we're legally married now.

165
00:10:25,780 --> 00:10:27,380
From this moment on,

166
00:10:28,020 --> 00:10:30,820
I am Xu Wanxin's rightful husband.

167
00:10:31,380 --> 00:10:33,299
I can stand by her side openly

168
00:10:33,300 --> 00:10:34,860
and do everything for her.

169
00:10:35,580 --> 00:10:36,460
But

170
00:10:36,660 --> 00:10:37,820
no one asked you.

171
00:10:38,060 --> 00:10:39,500
I just felt like saying it.

172
00:10:47,420 --> 00:10:50,900
Are you going to tell her
that you're the founder of Qingniao?

173
00:10:54,420 --> 00:10:56,980
Qingniao's cooperation with Minghui
has always existed.

174
00:10:58,020 --> 00:11:00,140
I don't want things between us
to get complicated

175
00:11:00,260 --> 00:11:03,500
because of this investment.

176
00:11:06,180 --> 00:11:08,500
Wanxin has too much to deal with.

177
00:11:08,940 --> 00:11:10,700
When everything settles,

178
00:11:13,660 --> 00:11:15,100
I'll tell her.

179
00:11:20,180 --> 00:11:22,580
Mr. Lover, you should be acting
in romance dramas.

180
00:11:26,180 --> 00:11:28,140
Anyway, congratulations, Mr. Gu.

181
00:11:28,420 --> 00:11:29,860
You got what you wanted.

182
00:11:30,780 --> 00:11:32,620
Wishing you and Miss Xu Wanxin

183
00:11:33,420 --> 00:11:34,659
a pleasant cooperation.

184
00:11:34,660 --> 00:11:35,500
No.

185
00:11:35,780 --> 00:11:37,380
A happy, long marriage.

186
00:11:38,420 --> 00:11:39,500
I'll take that.

187
00:11:47,720 --> 00:11:52,480
(Shen Gu, Xu Wanxin)

188
00:11:58,960 --> 00:11:59,970
Congratulations.

189
00:12:00,070 --> 00:12:01,180
Congratulations.

190
00:12:03,540 --> 00:12:04,740
Everyone,

191
00:12:04,820 --> 00:12:05,579
today

192
00:12:05,580 --> 00:12:07,779
is my daughter Lin Shuyi's

193
00:12:07,780 --> 00:12:09,819
18th birthday.

194
00:12:09,820 --> 00:12:12,940
Before she leaves for Europe to study,

195
00:12:13,340 --> 00:12:14,620
I hereby announce

196
00:12:15,220 --> 00:12:19,420
a marriage alliance
between the Lin and Shen families.

197
00:12:22,420 --> 00:12:23,300
Mr. Lin.

198
00:12:24,420 --> 00:12:26,540
I entrust the Lin family's trade

199
00:12:28,220 --> 00:12:30,140
to you.

200
00:12:30,820 --> 00:12:31,940
Thank you, Mr. Lin.

201
00:12:40,157 --> 00:12:41,620
You look beautiful today.

202
00:12:48,820 --> 00:12:50,819
A union of two families.

203
00:12:50,820 --> 00:12:52,579
A pact will be signed.

204
00:12:52,580 --> 00:12:54,419
May your marriage be everlasting

205
00:12:54,420 --> 00:12:56,140
and you be perfectly matched.

206
00:12:56,300 --> 00:12:58,459
The peach blossoms in full bloom

207
00:12:58,460 --> 00:13:00,380
reveal the perfect time for marriage.

208
00:13:00,460 --> 00:13:02,699
May your descendants flourish
like trailing vines,

209
00:13:02,700 --> 00:13:04,280
generation after generation.

210
00:13:04,280 --> 00:13:06,400
Let your vow to grow old together
be set down in writing,

211
00:13:06,400 --> 00:13:08,140
like a blessed union

212
00:13:08,420 --> 00:13:10,299
inscribed on a romantic red leaf,

213
00:13:10,300 --> 00:13:12,240
and recorded
in the Book of Devoted Mandarin Ducks.

214
00:13:14,300 --> 00:13:15,620
Here is the certificate.

215
00:13:52,820 --> 00:13:53,780
You're here.

216
00:13:55,860 --> 00:13:56,740
Wanxin.

217
00:13:57,100 --> 00:13:57,539
Come.

218
00:13:57,540 --> 00:13:58,660
Let's talk outside.

219
00:14:05,620 --> 00:14:07,700
This is my favorite soup.

220
00:14:08,820 --> 00:14:10,140
You're the best.

221
00:14:10,460 --> 00:14:12,020
Don't change the subject.

222
00:14:14,700 --> 00:14:17,140
It's only been half a day,
and you've gotten married.

223
00:14:18,580 --> 00:14:20,099
What happened?

224
00:14:20,100 --> 00:14:22,540
Didn't we say
we'd figure things out together?

225
00:14:25,140 --> 00:14:26,979
Grandfather might wake up soon.

226
00:14:26,980 --> 00:14:28,859
If he finds out you married Shen Hao...

227
00:14:28,860 --> 00:14:30,180
It's Shen Gu.

228
00:14:37,240 --> 00:14:39,960
(Shen Gu, Xu Wanxin)

229
00:14:41,220 --> 00:14:42,500
Shen Gu?

230
00:14:42,510 --> 00:14:44,300
The Shen Madam Song mentioned?

231
00:14:46,580 --> 00:14:47,740
Why?

232
00:14:48,340 --> 00:14:50,219
He was the one
who proposed cooperation first.

233
00:14:50,220 --> 00:14:52,140
He came back to Gang City
because of Shen Tingyuan.

234
00:14:53,220 --> 00:14:54,620
After I learned

235
00:14:54,820 --> 00:14:57,300
he's the largest shareholder of Junlin,

236
00:14:58,060 --> 00:14:59,860
I proposed marriage to him.

237
00:15:00,420 --> 00:15:01,859
I need his power

238
00:15:01,860 --> 00:15:04,140
to fight against
Shen Tingyuan's takeover.

239
00:15:06,620 --> 00:15:07,780
But

240
00:15:07,980 --> 00:15:09,540
it's only been half a day.

241
00:15:09,820 --> 00:15:11,740
You made a huge decision just like that?

242
00:15:13,140 --> 00:15:14,780
Do you even know him?

243
00:15:15,300 --> 00:15:17,099
Do you know his past?

244
00:15:17,100 --> 00:15:19,219
Do you know his real intentions?

245
00:15:19,220 --> 00:15:21,380
What if he turns out
to be another Shen Hao?

246
00:15:21,620 --> 00:15:24,140
It's just a contract marriage.

247
00:15:24,540 --> 00:15:26,140
We've agreed

248
00:15:26,220 --> 00:15:28,420
that we can divorce
once our goals are achieved.

249
00:15:28,700 --> 00:15:30,020
No matter what,

250
00:15:30,580 --> 00:15:32,940
I can't let Uncle Zhaohui
and Shen Tingyuan succeed.

251
00:15:32,980 --> 00:15:35,780
I have to stabilize Minghui
before Grandfather wakes up.

252
00:15:36,300 --> 00:15:38,140
I have to protect everything
my family has built.

253
00:15:51,460 --> 00:15:54,020
I just hoped you'd get married

254
00:15:54,540 --> 00:15:56,140
for love

255
00:15:56,980 --> 00:15:58,540
and to someone truly worth it.

256
00:16:00,980 --> 00:16:02,140
I know.

257
00:16:09,860 --> 00:16:11,180
It's strange.

258
00:16:16,620 --> 00:16:18,420
The man in my dreams

259
00:16:22,980 --> 00:16:24,300
was Shen Gu.

260
00:16:32,340 --> 00:16:34,600
(Gang City Marriage Registry)
Please confirm the validity of your documents

261
00:16:34,600 --> 00:16:36,419
and verify that the names

262
00:16:36,420 --> 00:16:37,219
and ID numbers

263
00:16:37,220 --> 00:16:39,180
match exactly.

264
00:16:41,820 --> 00:16:42,940
- No problem.
- No problem.

265
00:16:44,420 --> 00:16:48,819
I call upon all persons here
present to witness that I,

266
00:16:48,820 --> 00:16:52,219
Shen Gu, take thee, Xu Wanxin,

267
00:16:52,220 --> 00:16:54,740
to be my lawful wedded wife.

268
00:16:57,940 --> 00:16:59,180
- I do.
- I do.

269
00:17:00,100 --> 00:17:00,419
Alright.

270
00:17:00,420 --> 00:17:02,300
Please sign the form.

271
00:17:34,520 --> 00:17:42,000
(Shen Gu, Xu Wanxin)

272
00:18:15,140 --> 00:18:20,930
♪Tonight the rain falls soft and slow♪

273
00:18:22,210 --> 00:18:28,010
♪Blending with letters left unread
drifting through the air♪

274
00:18:28,710 --> 00:18:34,100
♪You turn and look back at me♪

275
00:18:35,220 --> 00:18:40,710
♪In those same eyes familiar tears
quietly appear♪

276
00:18:41,570 --> 00:18:47,220
♪It feels like we have carried so much♪

277
00:18:48,500 --> 00:18:53,960
♪So many questions time itself
could not make clear♪

278
00:18:55,080 --> 00:19:00,400
♪The moment you walked into my life♪

279
00:19:01,550 --> 00:19:07,380
♪Every dream I had became something
I want with you near♪

280
00:19:07,750 --> 00:19:14,720
♪How many letters have I written
just for you?♪

281
00:19:14,830 --> 00:19:20,540
♪If only you could truly hear
what my heart is trying to say♪

282
00:19:21,200 --> 00:19:27,569
♪From this life on no distance
could keep us apart♪

283
00:19:27,570 --> 00:19:30,449
♪The promise we made♪

284
00:19:30,450 --> 00:19:34,139
♪Will find its way to be fulfilled
one day♪

285
00:19:34,140 --> 00:19:40,719
♪But I want more
than just that fleeting gaze♪

286
00:19:40,720 --> 00:19:47,130
♪Still I have not heard your answer♪

287
00:19:47,520 --> 00:19:53,859
♪Can we still rewrite the ending
we face?♪

288
00:19:53,860 --> 00:19:58,950
♪When regrets begin to turn around you
will hear it all♪

289
00:19:59,430 --> 00:20:02,450
♪Everything that leads me back to you♪
